  "title": "Hone",
  "description": "Unlock your PCs true potential, Hone provides you the tools to achieve ultimate gameplay & boost FPS by rescuing your PC from bloated software.",
  "longDescription": "<!--textBlock-->\n<!--title-->\n# *OPTIMIZE* **YOUR PC FOR GAMING**\n<!--text-->\nHone provides you the tools to achieve ultimate gameplay & boost FPS by rescuing your PC from bloated software\n\n<!--textBlock-->\n<!--title-->\n# **MAX OUT YOUR GAMEPLAY**\n<!--text-->\nDon't settle for mediocre gameplay. With Hone, you can unlock the full potential of your system and enjoy smooth, lag-free gaming. Our optimizer is packed with features designed to give you the best possible gaming experience.\n\n<!--textBlock-->\n<!--title-->\n# **SMOOTHER GAMEPLAY HAS NEVER BEEN SIMPLER.**\n<!--text-->\nYou can optimize your PC with one click, all changes are fully revertible, you can choose what to switch on and off. Hone backups gives you peace of mind, the risk free optimizer.\n\n<!--textBlock-->\n<!--title-->\n# **WHAT YOU CAN ACHIEVE**\n<!--text-->\nUsing Hone to optimise your PC & game settings you can achieve FPS boosts similar to these based on our benchmarks:\n\n- Valorant **+51%**\n- Fortnite **+36%**\n- Rocket League **+35%**\n- League Of Legends **+30%**\n- Team Fortress 2 **+39%**\n- Counter-Strike: Global Offensive **+45%**\n- Destiny 2 **+27%**\n",
